case_circumstances: The remains of an unidentified female homicide victim were found down the side of Highway 9 in the hills above Saratoga, Ca. in an area near Booker Creek Road.  She is estimated to have been 15-24 years of age with brown colored hair and a petite build.  It is estimated she died sometime between April 2014 and December 2014 which is when her remains were found.  Anyone with information is asked to contact the Santa Clara County Sheriff's Office Investigations Division at (408) 808-4500 or the Anonymous Tip Line at (408) 808-4431.
